WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:02.400
You are not a kitten

2
00:00:03.266 --> 00:00:04.700
Not a puppy either

3
00:00:04.766 --> 00:00:06.200
You are my family.

4
00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.300
You are my one and only family

5
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:11.633
It was and always will be.

6
00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.966
You are my one and only friend.

7
00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:22.133
Lan Lan

8
00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:23.866
Are you hungry?

9
00:00:24.866 --> 00:00:26.266
I'll cook noodles for you to eat

10
00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:32.500
Your favorite food is my sister's noodles

11
00:00:32.766 --> 00:00:34.800
Eat it while it's hot

12
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:38.066
girl

13
00:00:38.066 --> 00:00:40.166
How dare you throw my precious spice in there?

14
00:00:40.166 --> 00:00:41.300
Give me a good reflection

15
00:00:57.733 --> 00:00:58.633
Wait for me.

16
00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:04.800
You're hungry! Eat!

17
00:01:06.100 --> 00:01:07.166
Let you eat

18
00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:08.466
Don't eat, I'll beat you up

19
00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:12.066
How was it?

20
00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:15.900
Brother, the noodles you cooked are the best noodles I have ever eaten

21
00:01:16.566 --> 00:01:18.466
Then of course it's not difficult for you

22
00:01:18.466 --> 00:01:19.800
And I did it the first time.

23
00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:21.966
If you want to eat it in the future, tell me and I will make it for you.

24
00:01:25.666 --> 00:01:27.233
Why don't you eat it?

25
00:01:27.766 --> 00:01:30.866
Liu Jingchi, I don't like noodles anymore

